# Dataset Information

The dataset used in this project was obtained from Kaggle.

Dataset:
General Mental Health and Lifestyle Dataset

The dataset was not uploaded directly to this repository to avoid potential licensing and distribution issues.

You can download the dataset here:

https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/mabubakrsiddiq/general-mental-health-and-lifestyle-dataset?resource=download

After downloading, place the dataset file inside this `data/` folder before running the notebook.
